<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Sports Website</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>
<style>
    /* General Styles */
    body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        color: #333;
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
    }

    header {
        background: #8fdea4;
        color: black;
        padding: 10px;
        position:sticky;
        top:0;
    }

    nav {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
    }

    .logo {
        font-size: 1.8em;
        font-weight: bold;
    }

    nav ul {
        list-style: none;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        display: flex;
    }

    nav ul li {
        margin-left: 20px;
        font-weight: 100;
    }



    nav ul li a {
        color: black;
        text-decoration: none;
        transition: color 0.3s;
        font-size: 20px;
    }

    nav ul li a:hover {
        color: white;
        padding: 2px;
        background-color: grey;
        border-radius: 5px;
    }

    #hero {
        background: url('https://www.shutterstock.com/image-vector/colorful-concept-sports-silhouettes-sport-600nw-2378868431.jpg') no-repeat center center/cover;
        color: rgb(59, 2, 2);
        text-align: center;
        padding: 100px 20px;
        opacity:0.69;
    }

    .hero-content {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .hero-content h1 {
        font-size: 3em;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        padding-top: 150px;
    }

    .hero-content p {
        font-size: 1.2em;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .cta {
        background: #ff6347;
        color: #fff;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
        transition: background 0.3s;
    }

    .cta:hover {
        background: #ff4500;
    }

    #features {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-around;
        padding: 50px 20px;
        background: #fff;
        flex-direction: row;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .feature {
        max-width: 300px;
        text-align: center;
        border: 2px solid #000; /* Adjusted border */
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); /* Optional: Add some shadow for better visual */
        padding: 20px; /* Optional: Add padding inside the box */
        margin: 20px; /* Optional: Add margin between the boxes */
        background-color: #fff; /* Optional: Set background color */
        border-radius: 10px; /* Optional: Add rounded corners */
    }

    .feature h2 {
        font-size: 2em;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    #feedback {
        text-align: center;
        background-color:#fff;
    }

    #feedback input {
        padding: 60px;
        border-radius: 20px;
    }

    footer {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px;
        background: #333;
        color: #fff;
    }
</style>
<body>
    <header>
        <nav>
            <div class="logo">SportsZone</div>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="#hero">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="#features">Features</a></li>
                <li><a href="#feedback">Contact</a></li>
                <li><a href="login">Login</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>
    <section id="hero">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1>Welcome to SportsZone</h1>
            <p>Your ultimate destination for sports news and updates</p>
            <a href="login" class="cta">Get Started</a>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section id="features">
        <div class="feature">
            <h2>Sports</h2>
            <p>The admin can add the sports.the added sports can be viewed and played by the players.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
            <h2>Create Sessions</h2>
            <p>Both Admin and Player can create a session for a game at a particular time period.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
            <h2>Join Sessions</h2>
            <p>Admin can also join the sessions to play the sport and also can able to delete the session.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
            <h2>Password Change</h2>
            <p>The player and the Admin can change the password by clicking the button provided in their interface.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
            <h2>User Integrity</h2>
            <p>We save the user details and passwords in a encrypted way.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
            <h2>Match Schedules</h2>
            <p>Never miss a game with our comprehensive schedules</p>
        </div>
    </section>
    <div id="feedback">
        <p>Your description here</p>
        <form id="feedbackForm">
            <input type="text" placeholder="Type here...." id="feedbackInput" name="feedback">
            <button type="submit" onclick="alert('feedback saved')">Submit</button>
        </form>
    </div>
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 SportsZone. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
<script>
    document.getElementById('feedbackForm').addEventListener('submit', function(event) {
        event.preventDefault(); // Prevent form submission
        var feedbackInput = document.getElementById('feedbackInput');
        console.log('Feedback submitted: ' + feedbackInput.value); 
        feedbackInput.value = '';
    });
</script>
</html>